# --- v2 additions ---

# Raw EMBER2018 download (1.6GB+ tar/tar.bz2), never meant to be committed,
# regenerate data/dataset_pe_v2_full.csv from it via the data-build step
# documented in README.md if needed again.
ember_dataset_2018_2.tar.bz2
ember_dataset_2018_2.tar/

# Large derived v2 CSV (129MB), regenerable from the EMBER tar via
# data_pipeline/build_dataset.py, not meant to be committed. Only the
# trained model file (models/classical_pipeline.joblib, tracked, see
# below) needs to be in the repo for Streamlit Cloud to deploy, it does
# not run notebooks. No separate train/val/test split files exist, every
# notebook that needs a split (04/05/06) derives the identical rows
# inline from this one file using a fixed RANDOM_STATE.
data/dataset_pe_v2_full.csv

# Intermediate v2 model candidates from 04/05 (comparison-only, not what
# app.py loads). Only models/classical_pipeline.joblib is the deployed
# artifact and needs to stay tracked.
models/rf_v2.joblib
models/xgb_v2.joblib
models/lgbm_v2.joblib
models/mlp_v2.keras
models/mlp_v2_scaler.joblib
models/deployed_mlp_v2.keras
models/deployed_mlp_v2_scaler.joblib
